description:
all the stories currently have some padding around, storybook has an option to use fullscreen layout

Changing `.storybook/preview.js` to

```
export const parameters = {
  layout: 'fullscreen',
  options: {
    storySort: (a, b) => a[1].id.localeCompare(b[1].id),
  },
};
``` 
should solve it. 

Then this file should be obsolete: `opengeoweb/libs/core/.storybook/preview-body.html`
